cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.IR, cs.CYBER, cs.DL 

Reasoning: The paper analyzes the spread of information (cascades) in Yelp reviews, which involves social influence and network analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SOC (Computational Social Science). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques to predict the size of cascades, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the possibility of accurately predicting cascades, which could involve machine learning and deep learning techniques, making cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity) and cs.DL (Machine Learning) possible sub-categories as well.
